{
  "video_id": "McxUiTl61nY",
  "title": "An astronaut's story of curiosity, perspective and change | Leland Melvin",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12221.0,
      "end_time": 15317.0,
      "text": "[This talk contains mature content]"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16770.0,
      "end_time": 21790.0,
      "text": "In 1969, I was standing behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21103.0,
      "end_time": 23976.0,
      "text": "a Sylvania black-and-white television set."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24640.0,
      "end_time": 27800.0,
      "text": "Hearing about these things happening on the set in the front,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27824.0,
      "end_time": 28975.0,
      "text": "I was the guy, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28999.0,
      "end_time": 32110.0,
      "text": "moving the rabbit ears for my dad, and my sister and my mom."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32134.0,
      "end_time": 35629.0,
      "text": "\"Move over here, turn over here, move this way, we can't see the screen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36213.0,
      "end_time": 38252.0,
      "text": "And what they were watching"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38276.0,
      "end_time": 43522.0,
      "text": "was: \"One small step for a man, one giant leap for mankind.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43546.0,
      "end_time": 46882.0,
      "text": "Neil [Armstrong] and Buzz Aldrin were walking on the Moon."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47308.0,
      "end_time": 51149.0,
      "text": "And I was five years old in Lynchburg, Virginia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51173.0,
      "end_time": 54493.0,
      "text": "a skinny black kid in a kind of somewhat racist town."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55303.0,
      "end_time": 59468.0,
      "text": "And I was trying to figure out what I was going to do with my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 60366.0,
      "end_time": 62732.0,
      "text": "And my parents, you know, they were educators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62756.0,
      "end_time": 64790.0,
      "text": "they'd said that you can do anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65930.0,
      "end_time": 68106.0,
      "text": "But after that moon landing, all the kids in the neighborhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68130.0,
      "end_time": 70264.0,
      "text": "were like, \"You're going to be an astronaut?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70288.0,
      "end_time": 71490.0,
      "text": "I'm like, \"No.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71514.0,
      "end_time": 74713.0,
      "text": "I don't want a buzz cut, and I don't see someone who looks like me."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74717.0,
      "end_time": 76419.0,
      "text": "Because representation does matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76443.0,
      "end_time": 80259.0,
      "text": "And I knew that there was a guy"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80284.0,
      "end_time": 83363.0,
      "text": "five blocks down the street on Pierce Street"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83387.0,
      "end_time": 85521.0,
      "text": "who was training to play tennis."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85848.0,
      "end_time": 87314.0,
      "text": "And it was Arthur Ashe."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87832.0,
      "end_time": 90735.0,
      "text": "And my dad talked about his character, his discipline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90760.0,
      "end_time": 93300.0,
      "text": "his intelligence, his athleticism."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93540.0,
      "end_time": 94424.0,
      "text": "I wanted to be Arthur Ashe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94448.0,
      "end_time": 96613.0,
      "text": "I didn't want to be one of those moon guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97106.0,
      "end_time": 101589.0,
      "text": "And as I went on through this journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101614.0,
      "end_time": 105535.0,
      "text": "my dad, who was a school teacher, he played in a band,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105559.0,
      "end_time": 108320.0,
      "text": "he did all these things to make money for my sister and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108344.0,
      "end_time": 109655.0,
      "text": "to take piano lessons"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109679.0,
      "end_time": 111797.0,
      "text": "and do these different things with education."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111821.0,
      "end_time": 117740.0,
      "text": "And he one day decides to drive up into the driveway with this bread truck."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118356.0,
      "end_time": 122133.0,
      "text": "And I'm thinking, \"OK, bread truck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 122157.0,
      "end_time": 125133.0,
      "text": "me delivering bread while my dad's driving the truck.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 125157.0,
      "end_time": 127768.0,
      "text": "I'm like, \"OK, I'm going to be a bread guy now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127792.0,
      "end_time": 130411.0,
      "text": "But he says, \"This is our camper.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131800.0,
      "end_time": 134792.0,
      "text": "I'm like, \"Dude, come one, I can read: 'Merita Bread and Rolls'"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134816.0,
      "end_time": 136354.0,
      "text": "on the side of this truck."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136378.0,
      "end_time": 140297.0,
      "text": "And he says, \"No, we're going to build this into our camper.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141187.0,
      "end_time": 145600.0,
      "text": "And over that summer, we rewired the entire electrical system."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145483.0,
      "end_time": 148133.0,
      "text": "We plumbed a propane tank to a Coleman stove,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148157.0,
      "end_time": 150601.0,
      "text": "we built bunk beds that flip down."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150625.0,
      "end_time": 155774.0,
      "text": "We were turning this into our summer vacation launch pad, escape pod,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155798.0,
      "end_time": 158565.0,
      "text": "this thing that could take us out of Lynchburg."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 159614.0,
      "end_time": 162214.0,
      "text": "And before that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163376.0,
      "end_time": 167312.0,
      "text": "I was actually raped at five by some neighbors."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168574.0,
      "end_time": 170998.0,
      "text": "And I didn't tell anyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 171220.0,
      "end_time": 174489.0,
      "text": "because I had friends that didn't have fathers."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174887.0,
      "end_time": 176848.0,
      "text": "And I knew that my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 176872.0,
      "end_time": 179840.0,
      "text": "would have killed the people that did that to his son."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 179864.0,
      "end_time": 182464.0,
      "text": "And I didn't want my father to be gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182959.0,
      "end_time": 187441.0,
      "text": "So as we got in this bread truck and escaped from Lynchburg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 187465.0,
      "end_time": 189668.0,
      "text": "it was my time with my dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189692.0,
      "end_time": 191926.0,
      "text": "And we went to the Smoky Mountains"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 191950.0,
      "end_time": 193997.0,
      "text": "and looked at the purple mountains' majesty."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 194210.0,
      "end_time": 196563.0,
      "text": "And we walked along the beach in Myrtle Beach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 196587.0,
      "end_time": 199698.0,
      "text": "and this thing was transformative."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200298.0,
      "end_time": 203933.0,
      "text": "It showed me what it meant to be an explorer, at a very early age."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 204433.0,
      "end_time": 207815.0,
      "text": "And I suppressed all that negativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207839.0,
      "end_time": 209500.0,
      "text": "all that trauma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 209290.0,
      "end_time": 211469.0,
      "text": "because I was learning to be an explorer."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 211910.0,
      "end_time": 214965.0,
      "text": "And a little bit later, my mother gave me an age-inappropriate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214989.0,
      "end_time": 216624.0,
      "text": "non-OSHA-certified chemistry set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216648.0,
      "end_time": 217811.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 217835.0,
      "end_time": 221728.0,
      "text": "where I created the most incredible explosion in her living room."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221752.0,
      "end_time": 223213.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223237.0,
      "end_time": 224975.0,
      "text": "And so I knew I could be a chemist."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 224999.0,
      "end_time": 227420.0,
      "text": "So as I went on this journey through a high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227444.0,
      "end_time": 229460.0,
      "text": "and I went to college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 229700.0,
      "end_time": 232189.0,
      "text": "and I got a football scholarship to play football in college."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 232213.0,
      "end_time": 235721.0,
      "text": "And I knew that I could be a chemist, because I'd already blown stuff up."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 235745.0,
      "end_time": 237379.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 237403.0,
      "end_time": 240784.0,
      "text": "And when I graduated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 240808.0,
      "end_time": 243382.0,
      "text": "I got drafted to the Detroit Lions."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 243406.0,
      "end_time": 245612.0,
      "text": "But I pulled a hamstring in training camp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 245636.0,
      "end_time": 248993.0,
      "text": "and so what every former NFL player does, they go work for NASA, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 249170.0,
      "end_time": 250311.0,
      "text": "So I went to work for NASA."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 250335.0,
      "end_time": 251336.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 251360.0,
      "end_time": 254453.0,
      "text": "And this friend of mine said, \"Leland, you'd be great astronaut.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 254477.0,
      "end_time": 257361.0,
      "text": "I just laughed at him, I was like, \"Yeah, me, an astronaut?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257385.0,
      "end_time": 259805.0,
      "text": "You know that Neil and Buzz thing from back in '69?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 259829.0,
      "end_time": 262396.0,
      "text": "And he handed me an application, and I looked at it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 262420.0,
      "end_time": 263682.0,
      "text": "and I didn't fill it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263706.0,
      "end_time": 268665.0,
      "text": "And that same year, another friend of mine filled out the application"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 268689.0,
      "end_time": 269839.0,
      "text": "and he got in."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 270372.0,
      "end_time": 271772.0,
      "text": "And I said to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 272790.0,
      "end_time": 275951.0,
      "text": "\"If NASA's letting knuckleheads like that be astronauts,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 275975.0,
      "end_time": 277149.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277173.0,
      "end_time": 278578.0,
      "text": "\"maybe I can be one, too.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 278602.0,
      "end_time": 282308.0,
      "text": "So the next selection, I filled out the application, and I got in."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282333.0,
      "end_time": 286142.0,
      "text": "And I didn't know what it meant to be an astronaut:"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 286166.0,
      "end_time": 288745.0,
      "text": "the training, the simulations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 288769.0,
      "end_time": 291839.0,
      "text": "all these things to get you ready for this countdown:"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 291863.0,
      "end_time": 293863.0,
      "text": "three, two, one, liftoff."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 294427.0,
      "end_time": 299877.0,
      "text": "And in 2007, I was in Space Shuttle \"Atlantis,\" careening off the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 299901.0,
      "end_time": 303435.0,
      "text": "traveling at 17,500 miles per hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 303880.0,
      "end_time": 305800.0,
      "text": "And eight and a half minutes later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 305824.0,
      "end_time": 309151.0,
      "text": "the main engines cut off, and we're now floating in space."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 309519.0,
      "end_time": 312472.0,
      "text": "And I push off and float over to the window,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 312496.0,
      "end_time": 314551.0,
      "text": "and I can see the Caribbean."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 314575.0,
      "end_time": 318205.0,
      "text": "And I need new definitions of blue to describe the colors that I see."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 318560.0,
      "end_time": 322723.0,
      "text": "Azure, indigo, navy blue, medium navy blue, turquoise"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 322747.0,
      "end_time": 325643.0,
      "text": "don't do any justice to what I see with my eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 326151.0,
      "end_time": 329860.0,
      "text": "And my job on this mission was to install"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 329110.0,
      "end_time": 332501.0,
      "text": "this two-billion dollar Columbus laboratory."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 333117.0,
      "end_time": 334800.0,
      "text": "It was a research laboratory"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 334824.0,
      "end_time": 337427.0,
      "text": "for materials research, for human research."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 337737.0,
      "end_time": 341860.0,
      "text": "And I reached into the payload bay of the space shuttle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 341110.0,
      "end_time": 343594.0,
      "text": "grabbed out this big module,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 343618.0,
      "end_time": 347440.0,
      "text": "and I used the robotic arm and I attached it to the space station."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 347962.0,
      "end_time": 351788.0,
      "text": "And the European team have been waiting 10 years for this thing to get installed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 351812.0,
      "end_time": 356386.0,
      "text": "so I'm sure everyone in Europe was like, \"Leland! Leland! Leland!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 356410.0,
      "end_time": 357800.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 357824.0,
      "end_time": 361402.0,
      "text": "And so this moment happened, this was our primary mission objective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 361426.0,
      "end_time": 362575.0,
      "text": "it was done."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 363600.0,
      "end_time": 365863.0,
      "text": "And I had this big sigh of relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 367189.0,
      "end_time": 370355.0,
      "text": "But then, Peggy Whitson, the first female commander,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 370379.0,
      "end_time": 372435.0,
      "text": "she invited us over to the Russian segment."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 372459.0,
      "end_time": 375308.0,
      "text": "And the space station's about the size of a football field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 375332.0,
      "end_time": 378863.0,
      "text": "with solar panel and trusses and all of these modules."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 379427.0,
      "end_time": 382491.0,
      "text": "And she says, \"Leland, you go get the rehydrated vegetables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 382515.0,
      "end_time": 383729.0,
      "text": "we have the meat.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 383753.0,
      "end_time": 387522.0,
      "text": "So we float over with the bag of vegetables, all rehydrated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 387546.0,
      "end_time": 388695.0,
      "text": "and we get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 389467.0,
      "end_time": 390789.0,
      "text": "And there's this moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 390813.0,
      "end_time": 395133.0,
      "text": "where I get [transported] back to my mother's kitchen."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 395157.0,
      "end_time": 397856.0,
      "text": "You can smell the beef and barley heating up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 397880.0,
      "end_time": 401633.0,
      "text": "you can smell the food, the colors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 401657.0,
      "end_time": 404554.0,
      "text": "and there are people there from all around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 404578.0,
      "end_time": 406164.0,
      "text": "It's like a Benetton commercial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 406189.0,
      "end_time": 410149.0,
      "text": "you know, you have African American, Asian American, French, German, Russian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 410173.0,
      "end_time": 411498.0,
      "text": "the first female commander,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 411522.0,
      "end_time": 415317.0,
      "text": "breaking bread at 17,500 miles per hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 415341.0,
      "end_time": 417667.0,
      "text": "going around the planet every 90 minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 417691.0,
      "end_time": 420597.0,
      "text": "seeing a sunrise and a sunset every 45."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 421127.0,
      "end_time": 423754.0,
      "text": "And Peggy would say, \"Hey, Leland, try some of this,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 423778.0,
      "end_time": 425579.0,
      "text": "and she'd float it over to my mouth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 425603.0,
      "end_time": 427832.0,
      "text": "and I'd catch it and we'd go back and forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 427856.0,
      "end_time": 433150.0,
      "text": "And we're doing all of this while listening to Sade's \"Smooth Operator.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 433390.0,
      "end_time": 434390.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 434640.0,
      "end_time": 436459.0,
      "text": "I mean, this is like blowing my mind, you know."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 436483.0,
      "end_time": 437578.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 437602.0,
      "end_time": 441220.0,
      "text": "And I float over to the window, and I look down at the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 441460.0,
      "end_time": 444780.0,
      "text": "and I see all of humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 444499.0,
      "end_time": 447221.0,
      "text": "And my perspective changes at that moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 447245.0,
      "end_time": 450124.0,
      "text": "because, I'm flying over Lynchburg, Virginia, my home town,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 450148.0,
      "end_time": 452134.0,
      "text": "and my family's probably breaking bread."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 452158.0,
      "end_time": 454721.0,
      "text": "And five minutes later, we're flying over Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 454745.0,
      "end_time": 457348.0,
      "text": "where Leo Eyharts is looking down at his parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 457372.0,
      "end_time": 459173.0,
      "text": "probably having some wine and cheese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 459197.0,
      "end_time": 461610.0,
      "text": "and Yuri's looking off to Moscow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 461850.0,
      "end_time": 463630.0,
      "text": "and they're probably eating borscht or something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 463654.0,
      "end_time": 468681.0,
      "text": "But we're all having this moment where we see our respective families"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 468705.0,
      "end_time": 472871.0,
      "text": "working together as one civilization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 472896.0,
      "end_time": 475253.0,
      "text": "at 17,500 miles per hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 476245.0,
      "end_time": 479780.0,
      "text": "My perspective shifted cognitively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 479102.0,
      "end_time": 480435.0,
      "text": "it changed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 480459.0,
      "end_time": 482919.0,
      "text": "And when I think about being that little skinny boy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 482943.0,
      "end_time": 486300.0,
      "text": "from sometimes racist Lynchburg, Virginia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 486324.0,
      "end_time": 490451.0,
      "text": "I would never have had that perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 490475.0,
      "end_time": 493459.0,
      "text": "to think about myself of being an astronaut,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 493483.0,
      "end_time": 496514.0,
      "text": "if my father hadn't taken us on a journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 496538.0,
      "end_time": 500399.0,
      "text": "in this radical craft that we built with our own two hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 502160.0,
      "end_time": 504230.0,
      "text": "When I came home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 504254.0,
      "end_time": 508952.0,
      "text": "I realized that perspective is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 508976.0,
      "end_time": 511421.0,
      "text": "that we all get and we all have."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 512236.0,
      "end_time": 514673.0,
      "text": "It's just how far do we open up our blinders"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 514697.0,
      "end_time": 517244.0,
      "text": "to see that shift and that change."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 517903.0,
      "end_time": 519702.0,
      "text": "And going back to the space station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 519726.0,
      "end_time": 524549.0,
      "text": "I think of, you know, Germans and Russians fighting Americans."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 525810.0,
      "end_time": 528250.0,
      "text": "We have these people living and working together."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 528382.0,
      "end_time": 532474.0,
      "text": "White folks, black folks, Russian folks, French folks, you know."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 532499.0,
      "end_time": 537600.0,
      "text": "All these different people coexisting in harmony as one race."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 538712.0,
      "end_time": 542959.0,
      "text": "And I think about the colors that I saw, the design of the modules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 542983.0,
      "end_time": 544563.0,
      "text": "the way that things fit together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 544587.0,
      "end_time": 548348.0,
      "text": "the way that it made us a community, our home."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 549221.0,
      "end_time": 553709.0,
      "text": "And so when I look up to space now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 553733.0,
      "end_time": 557473.0,
      "text": "and I have this newfound perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 557498.0,
      "end_time": 560685.0,
      "text": "on the space station going overhead and looking there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 560709.0,
      "end_time": 562501.0,
      "text": "and then looking back at my community"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 562525.0,
      "end_time": 565723.0,
      "text": "and seeing the people that I'm living and working with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 565748.0,
      "end_time": 567843.0,
      "text": "and coexisting with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 567867.0,
      "end_time": 573791.0,
      "text": "I think it's something that we all can do now, especially in these times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 573816.0,
      "end_time": 577538.0,
      "text": "to make sure that we have the right perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 578466.0,
      "end_time": 579660.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 579684.0,
      "end_time": 584314.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 584338.0,
      "end_time": 587828.0,
      "text": "Chee Pearlman: If you don't mind, could I just chat with you for a minute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 587852.0,
      "end_time": 590223.0,
      "text": "because they're going to set up some things here."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 590248.0,
      "end_time": 592550.0,
      "text": "And I get to have you all to myself, OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 592574.0,
      "end_time": 593784.0,
      "text": "Leland Melvin: Alright."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 594348.0,
      "end_time": 596165.0,
      "text": "CP: You guys don't get to hear this."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 596189.0,
      "end_time": 598267.0,
      "text": "So I have to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 598292.0,
      "end_time": 603454.0,
      "text": "that in my family, we watch a lot of space movies"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 603478.0,
      "end_time": 605363.0,
      "text": "about astronauts and stuff like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 605387.0,
      "end_time": 607402.0,
      "text": "I can't tell you why, but we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 607427.0,
      "end_time": 609212.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 609849.0,
      "end_time": 611925.0,
      "text": "The thing that I wanted to ask you, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 611949.0,
      "end_time": 615305.0,
      "text": "is that we were seeing this movie the other day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 615329.0,
      "end_time": 619221.0,
      "text": "and it was about one of the astronauts, one of your colleagues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 619245.0,
      "end_time": 622213.0,
      "text": "and before he went up into space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 622237.0,
      "end_time": 626396.0,
      "text": "they actually wrote an obituary, NASA wrote an obituary for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 626792.0,
      "end_time": 628642.0,
      "text": "And I was like, is that normal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 628666.0,
      "end_time": 630602.0,
      "text": "And is that part of the job?"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 630626.0,
      "end_time": 636160.0,
      "text": "Do you think about that peril that you're putting yourself in"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 636184.0,
      "end_time": 637478.0,
      "text": "as you go into space?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 637502.0,
      "end_time": 638800.0,
      "text": "LM: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 638824.0,
      "end_time": 641780.0,
      "text": "So, I don't remember anyone writing my obituary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 641102.0,
      "end_time": 643713.0,
      "text": "maybe that was an Apollo-day thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 643737.0,
      "end_time": 648267.0,
      "text": "But I do know that in the 135 shuttle flights that we've had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 648292.0,
      "end_time": 650943.0,
      "text": "the shuttle that I flew on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 650967.0,
      "end_time": 654737.0,
      "text": "we had two accidents that killed everyone on that mission."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 655292.0,
      "end_time": 658572.0,
      "text": "And we all know the perils and the risks that go along with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 658596.0,
      "end_time": 661435.0,
      "text": "but we're doing something that's much bigger than ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 661459.0,
      "end_time": 663600.0,
      "text": "and helping advance civilization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 663850.0,
      "end_time": 666181.0,
      "text": "so the risk is worth the reward."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 666515.0,
      "end_time": 669227.0,
      "text": "And we all feel that way when we get into that vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 669251.0,
      "end_time": 673967.0,
      "text": "ans strap into those million pounds of rocket fuel and go up to space."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 673991.0,
      "end_time": 676332.0,
      "text": "CP: Yeah, I've only seen the Hollywood version --"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 676356.0,
      "end_time": 678715.0,
      "text": "it looks pretty terrifying, I have to tell you."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 678739.0,
      "end_time": 679943.0,
      "text": "LM: You should go."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 679967.0,
      "end_time": 681117.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 681142.0,
      "end_time": 683879.0,
      "text": "CP: Yeah, my husband's told me that a few times."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 683903.0,
      "end_time": 685895.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 685919.0,
      "end_time": 687879.0,
      "text": "LM: One-way trip or two-way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 687903.0,
      "end_time": 689540.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 689780.0,
      "end_time": 691530.0,
      "text": "CP: That’s a bit of a debate in our house."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 691554.0,
      "end_time": 693180.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 693411.0,
      "end_time": 696883.0,
      "text": "I wanted to, if I may ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 697554.0,
      "end_time": 702786.0,
      "text": "You did touch on something that was very powerful and difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 702811.0,
      "end_time": 706472.0,
      "text": "which is, you spoke about this incident"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 706496.0,
      "end_time": 709200.0,
      "text": "that had happened to you when you were five years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 709440.0,
      "end_time": 710225.0,
      "text": "and that you were raped."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 710249.0,
      "end_time": 713451.0,
      "text": "And I just think that for you to be able to say those things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 713475.0,
      "end_time": 715602.0,
      "text": "you know, on the TED stage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 715626.0,
      "end_time": 718308.0,
      "text": "to be able to talk about that at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 718332.0,
      "end_time": 720268.0,
      "text": "is pretty fearless."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 720292.0,
      "end_time": 723157.0,
      "text": "And I wanted to get a sense from you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 723181.0,
      "end_time": 727428.0,
      "text": "is that something that you think is important for you to share that now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 727452.0,
      "end_time": 728895.0,
      "text": "to speak about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 728919.0,
      "end_time": 733470.0,
      "text": "LM: It's so important, especially for men, to talk about things that have happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 733710.0,
      "end_time": 734550.0,
      "text": "because we've been trained"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 734574.0,
      "end_time": 738760.0,
      "text": "and told by our society that we have to be so tough and so hard"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 738784.0,
      "end_time": 741609.0,
      "text": "and we can't tell of things that are happening to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 741633.0,
      "end_time": 745187.0,
      "text": "But I've had so many men contact me and tell me that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 745211.0,
      "end_time": 747260.0,
      "text": "\"You came through that, you got over that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 747284.0,
      "end_time": 749107.0,
      "text": "I'm going to get over my alcoholism,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 749131.0,
      "end_time": 751149.0,
      "text": "and these things that are going on in them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 751173.0,
      "end_time": 752776.0,
      "text": "because of what happened to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 752800.0,
      "end_time": 756450.0,
      "text": "And so we must share these stories, this is part of storytelling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 756700.0,
      "end_time": 759300.0,
      "text": "to heal us and to make us whole as a community."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 759324.0,
      "end_time": 761223.0,
      "text": "CP: That's wonderful."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 761247.0,
      "end_time": 766670.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 766694.0,
      "end_time": 770853.0,
      "text": "And you know, quite honestly, you spoke about perspective shift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 770877.0,
      "end_time": 775173.0,
      "text": "and that is a shift that I think we've been very slow to accept"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 775197.0,
      "end_time": 779620.0,
      "text": "and to be able to speak about that, so we thank you for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 779860.0,
      "end_time": 782231.0,
      "text": "We thank you for being the amazing astronaut that you are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 782255.0,
      "end_time": 784665.0,
      "text": "and thank you for coming to the TED stage, Leland."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 784690.0,
      "end_time": 786650.0,
      "text": "LM: Thank you so much, Chee."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 786890.0,
      "end_time": 787405.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}